How to bypass account ban 

1)If you got ban from xyz.com  try to see other domain like forms etc where you need the same account to login.

  you maybe able to login from forms.xyz.com and its a bypass I found it on a hackerone private program.



如何绕过帐户禁令

1)如果您被 xyz.com 禁止，请尝试查看其他域，例如需要使用相同帐户登录的表单等。

   您也许可以从 forms.xyz.com 登录，这是我在hacker one 私人程序上发现的一种绕过方式。